EUROPE -- DEFENSE; MILITARY FORCE REDUCTIONS; ARMS CONTROL; MILITARY TRAINING; 
UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY; NUCLEAR WEAPONS -- EUROPE; 
UNITED STATES -- MILITARY AID -- EUROPE 
</P>
