SAN DIEGO COUNTY DIGEST: SAN ONOFRE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
An unidentified pedestrian, about 20 years old, was killed at 5 a.m. Thursday 
as he was crossing northbound Interstate 5 near the San Onofre checkpoint, 
California Highway Patrol officials said. 
</P>
