<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA012789-0049 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 10662 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 27, 1989, Friday, San Diego County Edition 
