to sell by an incredibly good offer. GARY FRIEDMAN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
Lisa Berger: Spruce up your business long before you talk to a buyer. BERNIE 
BOSTON / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
