<P>
POLITICAL APPOINTMENTS; ATWOOD, DONALD J; GENERAL MOTORS CORP; GM HUGHES 
ELECTRONICS CORP; CURRIE, MALCOLM R; CORPORATE RESTRUCTURING 
</P>
